Package org.neo4j.storageengine.api.txstate

Interface EntityState

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    NodeState, RelationshipState
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EntityState.EmptyEntityState, EntityStateImpl, NodeStateImpl, RelationshipStateImpl
    public interface EntityState
    Represents the property changes to a node or relationship:
    • Added properties,
    • removed properties, and
    • changed property values.
